<collectingCountry box="[763,876,793,815]" name="Guatemala" pageId="22" pageNumber="1167">Guatemala</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="22.[151,1059,830,911]" pageId="22" pageNumber="1167">
E t y m o l o g y: The trivial name, 
<emphasis box="[551,658,830,851]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="1167">championi</emphasis>
, is a patronym dedicated to George Charles Champion for his dedicated efforts in enhancing our knowledge of Middle American beetles.
</paragraph>
